1024
00:34:38,285 --> 00:34:40,255
There are many tempting ingredients.

1025
00:34:40,588 --> 00:34:42,097
Your first dinner...

1026
00:34:43,125 --> 00:34:44,224
(The director is affected by the cold without exceptions.)

1027
00:34:44,225 --> 00:34:46,665
Your first dinner ingredient is...

1028
00:34:46,895 --> 00:34:48,564
Korean staple food, rice.

1029
00:34:48,565 --> 00:34:50,634
