- We need some rice.

1030
00:34:50,635 --> 00:34:51,765
(I like rice.)

1031
00:34:52,235 --> 00:34:54,334
I can make rice in a pot. It doesn't take long.

1032
00:34:54,335 --> 00:34:56,374
- Let's make porridge.
- We can cook rice in a pot fast.

1033
00:34:56,375 --> 00:34:59,844
