1069
00:36:07,575 --> 00:36:08,844
- Just do it.
- You can do it.

1070
00:36:08,845 --> 00:36:10,315
Don't try so hard.

1071
00:36:10,415 --> 00:36:11,914
- Do it unconsciously.
- Okay.

1072
00:36:11,915 --> 00:36:13,514
- Don't pressure me.
- Don't feel pressured.

1073
00:36:13,515 --> 00:36:16,084
- Don't pressure me.
- Stop talking. You'll spit on it.

1074
00:36:16,085 --> 00:36:17,524
- Here I go.
- Start.

1075
00:36:17,525 --> 00:36:18,525
I'll start.

1076
00:36:18,725 --> 00:36:20,254
- Just do it fast.
- He got it.

1077
00:36:20,255 --> 00:36:21,255
(Amazed)

1078
00:36:22,025 --> 00:36:23,294
(He ignites it easily.)

1079
00:36:23,295 --> 00:36:24,424
Just do it fast.

1080
00:36:24,425 --> 00:36:26,364
- He got it.
- One, two.

1081
00:36:26,365 --> 00:36:27,564
Endure the heat.

1082
