1083
00:36:30,235 --> 00:36:31,504
(Jong Min, even if it's hot,)

1084
00:36:31,505 --> 00:36:32,765
(you must endure it.)

1085
00:36:33,035 --> 00:36:34,674
(Shaking)

1086
00:36:34,675 --> 00:36:35,834
- Endure the heat.
- Gosh.

1087
00:36:35,835 --> 00:36:37,405
(Gosh, it's hot.)

1088
00:36:37,645 --> 00:36:39,445
I smell flesh burning.

1089
00:36:39,675 --> 00:36:41,344
You can't hold it like that.

1090
00:36:41,345 --> 00:36:42,545
Hold it this way.

1091
00:36:42,645 --> 00:36:45,885
(If he held it longer, it could've been dangerous.)

1092
00:36:46,115 --> 00:36:47,115
- I'll go.
- Start.

1093
00:36:47,115 --> 00:36:48,115
