1094
00:36:48,116 --> 00:36:49,185
Start right away.

1095
00:36:49,655 --> 00:36:52,624
- One, two, three. You got it.
- One, two, three.

1096
00:36:52,625 --> 00:36:54,295
- Success.
- It's very easy.

1097
00:36:54,425 --> 00:36:56,294
- Do it without thinking.
- It's easy. Do it without thinking.

1098
00:36:56,295 --> 00:36:57,694
- Just do it.
- DinDin.

1099
