- Do it how you usually do it.

1105
00:37:09,905 --> 00:37:11,145
Don't try to...

1106
00:37:12,475 --> 00:37:13,814
- What's wrong with you?
- Do it how you usually do it.

1107
00:37:13,815 --> 00:37:14,815
Don't make it hard.

1108
00:37:14,816 --> 00:37:16,614
- So I'll do the same.
- Okay.

1109
00:37:16,615 --> 00:37:18,145
- Don't feel pressured.
- Keep it safe.

1110
00:37:19,445 --> 00:37:22,984
- One, two, three. Success.
- He almost missed it.

1111
00:37:22,985 --> 00:37:25,255
- He got it.
- It could go out easily that way.

1112
00:37:25,700 --> 00:37:27,970
This is nerve-racking.

1113
00:37:27,995 --> 00:37:30,154
- Joon.
- I'll do it unconsciously.

1114
00:37:30,155 --> 00:37:31,864
- One, two, go.
