1120
00:37:43,447 --> 00:37:45,520
(You said that you could do it casually.)

1121
00:37:46,590 --> 00:37:48,119
- One, - He's good.

1122
00:37:48,120 --> 00:37:49,660
two, three.

1123
00:37:50,660 --> 00:37:52,630
I'm so happy.

1124
00:37:54,200 --> 00:37:56,257
What is he doing? Jae Won.

1125
00:37:56,282 --> 00:37:58,400
