- Right here.

1135
00:38:19,760 --> 00:38:21,090
- Come on.
- Of course, he can light a match.

1136
00:38:21,160 --> 00:38:22,160
- Here I go.
- Okay.

1137
00:38:22,160 --> 00:38:23,160
I'll start.

1138
