1150
00:38:49,520 --> 00:38:50,889
- He hasn't done it many times.
- What was that?

1151
00:38:50,890 --> 00:38:51,990
(Is this hard?)

1152
00:38:52,150 --> 00:38:54,360
- It ignites right away. Then why...
- I mean, why...

1153
00:38:55,160 --> 00:38:57,459
One, two, three.

1154
00:38:57,460 --> 00:38:59,030
