1188
00:39:58,750 --> 00:39:59,820
- Oh, that's a good idea.
- That's a good strategy.

1189
00:40:00,460 --> 00:40:01,859
- That's right.
- Show us how to trap a ball.

1190
00:40:01,860 --> 00:40:03,359
