- So I can just head the ball.

1202
00:40:21,940 --> 00:40:23,809
- Let us practice first.
- Okay.

1203
00:40:23,810 --> 00:40:24,980
The head doesn't count.

1204
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:26,580
- Oh, what?
- That's good.

1205
00:40:26,780 --> 00:40:27,919
