1208
00:40:32,760 --> 00:40:34,959
- Okay. That's good. He's good.
- Nice.

1209
00:40:34,960 --> 00:40:37,490
- We found what Jae Won is good at.
- We found it.

1210
00:40:37,560 --> 00:40:39,530
Can you make it look like I just joined them now?

1211
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:42,770
Go over there and come back with the ball.

1212
00:40:43,600 --> 00:40:45,070
- Hello.
- Welcome.

1213
00:40:46,670 --> 00:40:47,799
