1214
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:49,539
- Jae Won!
- How about a ball game?

1215
00:40:49,540 --> 00:40:50,870
- Sounds great.
- All right.

1216
00:40:50,970 --> 00:40:52,979
- Why didn't you come early?
- I had work to do.

1217
00:40:52,980 --> 00:40:55,309
We'll give you time to practice...

1218
00:40:55,310 --> 00:40:57,409
- Let's give it a try.
- and three attempts.

1219
00:40:57,410 --> 00:40:59,720
- This is easy.
- But we failed even in jegichagi.

1220
