Kicking a ball is much easier than kicking a jegi.

1221
00:41:02,790 --> 00:41:04,089
- Try it.
- Good. There you go.

1222
00:41:04,090 --> 00:41:05,619
- Kick it lightly.
- Let's go.

1223
00:41:05,620 --> 00:41:07,059
- Good. We have a chance.
- Exactly.

1224
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:08,420
- Save the ball.
- Save the ball.

1225
00:41:09,060 --> 00:41:10,989
- Keep it in the air.
- All right. There.

1226
00:41:10,990 --> 00:41:12,759
It's best we pass the ball to the person...

1227
00:41:12,760 --> 00:41:13,960
- on our left side.
- Right.

1228
00:41:14,260 --> 00:41:15,799
No. It's okay. This is practice.

1229
00:41:15,800 --> 00:41:17,429
Right. Let's see if it works.

1230
00:41:17,430 --> 00:41:18,499
There. That's good.

1231
00:41:18,500 --> 00:41:19,699
We just have to pass it gently. Keep going.

1232
00:41:19,700 --> 00:41:20,700
- Slowly.
- You know...

1233
00:41:21,740 --> 00:41:22,740
- Oh, no.
- Our tent.

